Battlefield 6 is here - and this is our initial video on what is an excellent release. Focusing on the PlayStation 5 version for now, Oliver goes into the plus and minus points of the campaign before moving onto a multiplayer focus, including 120Hz VRR performance. And what's with all the content download options and menu selections? In our next video, we'll be looking at the full range of consoles and modes and how they compare.
